description: DistIT AB engages in the acquisition, provision, and distribution of information technology products. The company acquires, owns and develops small distributors in the fields of IT, mobile, consumer electronics and data communication in the Nordic region. The company offers a range of computer accessories, switches, converters, cables, fiber optic cables, networking products, peripherals, accessories, elements of IT infrastructure and multimedia products under the DELTACO brand name. The firm offers its products to both private and corporate customers. The Deltaco group comprises around 20 medium-sized distributors, including SweDeltaco AB, Aurora Group A/S, UAB Sominis technology and Winther Wireless AB, among others. The Company’s main shareholders are Ribbskottet AB, Avanza Pension FAB and Catella Fondforvaltning AB.
